Visualizes include relationships between C/C++ source and header files
as a graph in DOT syntax. To generate a dependency graph, type the following:

1. $ cd ~/program/src

2. $ cppinclude2dot > include_dep.dot
3. $ dot -Tpng include_dep.dot > include_dep.png
or more easy: $ cppinclude2dot -t png -o include_dep.png 

To get more information type cppinclude2dot --help.